299
00:33:45,592 --> 00:33:53,632
It could be your husband, your wife, your
children, your relations, your friends, anybody,

300
00:33:53,632 --> 00:33:55,702
any Sahaja Yogi.

301
00:33:55,702 --> 00:33:58,722
But in the case of Shri Ganesha, it’s the
