nature –ed.]

312
00:35:05,502 --> 00:35:10,212
You are all realized souls now, you are all
saints.

313
00:35:10,212 --> 00:35:16,412
The false people are talking so big, and you
the people who have got something are still

314
00:35:16,412 --> 00:35:19,752
thinking, “My ego will come up, this will
happen.”

315
00:35:19,752 --> 00:35:25,632
No, no, you have the powers.

316
00:35:25,632 --> 00:35:36,452
But as you keep it under a manger, as Christ
has said, the light will go out.

317
00:35:36,452 --> 00:35:48,371
You have to give it to others, you have to
open it out.

318
00:35:48,371 --> 00:35:50,452
And that is how you will judge your state.

319
00:35:50,452 --> 00:35:53,102
“What is my state?

320
00:35:53,102 --> 00:35:55,172
Let’s see.

321
00:35:55,172 --> 00:35:58,262
Where am I?”

322
00:35:58,262 --> 00:36:05,752
That confidence, take it from Me, should be
with you.

323
00:36:05,752 --> 00:36:11,292
All of you have to work out this way.

324
00:36:11,292 --> 00:36:13,272
Very many…

